# Custom APIs

> **Note**: For information on how to implement custom routes in the project, see the [Custom Router Pattern](mdc:.cursor/rules/custom-router.mdc) rule.

## Authentication

- [Auth API](mdc:src/api/auth/controllers/auth.ts) - Authentication functions
  - OTP generation and verification
  - Login and account management
  - Password management
  - User self-information

## Shopping Cart

- [Cart API](mdc:src/api/cart/controllers/cart.ts) - Shopping cart functionality
  - Add/remove items from cart
  - Update quantities
  - Apply discounts
  - Cart checkout process

## Order Management

- [Order API](mdc:src/api/order/controllers/order.ts) - Order management
  - Order creation and processing
  - Order status updates
  - Payment processing
  - Order history and tracking

## User Management

- [Local User API](mdc:src/api/local-user/controllers/local-user.ts) - User account management
  - User registration and profile management
  - Account settings and preferences
  - Address book management

## Product Management

- [Product API](mdc:src/api/product/controllers/product.ts) - Product management
  - Product search and filtering
  - Product recommendations
  - Product review management

## Product Reviews

- [Product Review API](mdc:src/api/product-review/controllers/product-review.ts) - Product review management
  - [Custom Router](mdc:src/api/product-review/routes/custom-router.ts) defines these endpoints:
    - `POST /product-reviews/submit` - Submit or update a review (one per product per user)
    - `GET /product-reviews/user/me` - Get all reviews by the current user

## Product Likes/Favorites

- [Product Like API](mdc:src/api/product-like/controllers/product-like.ts) - Product favorites management
  - [Custom Router](mdc:src/api/product-like/routes/custom-router.ts) defines these endpoints:
    - `POST /product-likes/toggle` - Toggle a product as favorite
    - `GET /product-likes/user/me` - Get all products favorited by the current user

